<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Successfully Updated - PropertyRent</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .success-icon {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .checkmark {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #dcfce7;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #16a34a;
        }
        .features-list {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features-list h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #166534;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .features-list ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .features-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #15803d;
        }
        .login-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px 0 rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.39);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .login-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f7fafc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
            .header { padding: 30px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>PropertyRent</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Email Successfully Updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <div class="checkmark">âœ“</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Congratulations {{userName}}!</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>Your email address has been successfully updated and verified. This new email address is now the primary email for your PropertyRent account.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="features-list">
                <h3>What's Next:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use this new email address for all future logins</li>
                    <li>All notifications and updates will be sent here</li>
                    <li>Your account security has been maintained throughout the process</li>
                    <li>You can now access all PropertyRent features as usual</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="login-btn">
                    Login to Your Account
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p><strong>Important Security Note:</strong> Your previous email address is no longer associated with this account. If you need to change your email again in the future, you can do so from your account settings.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <p>Thank you for keeping your account information up to date. This helps us provide you with the best possible service.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Welcome to your updated PropertyRent experience!</p>
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyRent. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>